{"tid":2301732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"揮別宋仲基一年！宋慧喬超低胸滑出「傲人雙峰」狂曬事業線","createTime":"2020-11-26T13:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T16:08:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9efa4d156464db6fc2871c7f034d0f954f1df1","tid":2301732,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"南韓女神宋慧喬與宋仲基離婚後，生活重心一直都在工作上，接下Chaumet亞太區品牌大使後，賣力宣傳，今釋出她為聖誕節拍攝的一系列新照，超美膚況配上珠寶，其中一套平口洋裝令她露出超深事業線，粉絲紛紛狂讚：「女神回歸了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/26/2904327-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2F2904327-PH.jpg&h=9252a61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋慧喬超低胸最新代言照曝光，配上手寫祝福。（圖／CHAUMET提供）<br />\n<br />\n宋慧喬22日剛過39歲生日，絕美凍齡外貌根本看不出她實際年紀，她所代言的珠寶品牌Chaumet公開三張照片，分別穿上三套服裝配著不同珠寶，當中一套平口裝搭配Liens系列珠寶的造型，讓常秀美腿的她難得露出傲人事業線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/26/2904368-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F26%2F2904368-PH.jpg&h=02ac69a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1c84c11e5941a46e6fa5c84cf997d325dd457d3","tid":2301732,"uid":190187,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:54:04.000Z","msg":"超低胸喺邊？"},{"pid":"38f718a10e15e2341ada6a5ed80161b442e0516e","tid":2301732,"uid":28068,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"宋仲基真係賤人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bde38fea20cc28fe916413ee65de2be732a6bd0","tid":2301732,"uid":338422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f718a10e15e2341ada6a5ed80161b442e0516e","tid":2301732,"uid":28068,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"宋仲基真係賤人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"離婚原因係咩其實"},{"pid":"1d6e5444